gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 96, Raptors 88
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nets defeated the Raptors, 96-88. Dennis Schroder recorded 19 points, seven assists, and five rebounds for the Nets, with Trendon Watford adding 19 points and seven rebounds in the victory. Gary Trent Jr. tallied 18 points, two rebounds, and two assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Nets improve to 27-45, while the Raptors fall to 23-49.
